        <purpose>This dataset includes geographic distribution and molecular drivers of insecticide resistance in Ghanaian Anopheles populations. It informs strategic decision-making for insecticide choice, resistance management plans, and long-term malaria vector control policies in the face of evolving resistance patterns.</purpose>
